 <hr>                              
<a name="orig"><font size="+2">Original Java Specification Request (JSR)</font></a><p>
<font size="-1">
<A HREF="#1"> Identification</A> ? | ?
          <A HREF="#2"> Request</A>  ?| ?
          <A HREF="#3"> Contributions</A></font><p>


<A NAME="1"></A>
<P>
